## 📚 Useful Commands

Restart MariaDB:

```bash
sudo systemctl restart mariadb
```

Stop MariaDB:

```bash
sudo systemctl stop mariadb
```

Check service status:

```bash
sudo systemctl status mariadb
```

View MariaDB version:

```bash
mysql --version
```

